    "description": "🌥️  Soar through the skies like never before and restore balance to the universe with Sky Climb! 💫<br>This first-person adventure brings classic platforming to VR, featuring an intuitive arm-based locomotion mechanism that allows you to fling yourself from one cube to another in low gravity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🟪 Single Player Campaign</h2>An adventure with 8 unique worlds, comprising 74 levels complete with boss encounters and power-ups.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/5bf62c89a0f3224c215a1ea252833329.poster.avif?t=1730396331\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/5bf62c89a0f3224c215a1ea252833329.webm?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/5bf62c89a0f3224c215a1ea252833329.mp4?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🟪 Multiplayer  Championship</h2>Challenge your friends in the Online mode, supporting up to 6 players and 24 bots in races, hoop-collecting or shooting challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/454ced614e59e3ea4b273f5c5398c138.poster.avif?t=1730396331\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/454ced614e59e3ea4b273f5c5398c138.webm?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/454ced614e59e3ea4b273f5c5398c138.mp4?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🟪 Personalize Your Climber</h2>Collect tons of customization options and stand out from the crowd!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/fa90ab0952df810fd7ad23bed3a6f0f4.poster.avif?t=1730396331\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/fa90ab0952df810fd7ad23bed3a6f0f4.webm?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/fa90ab0952df810fd7ad23bed3a6f0f4.mp4?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🟪 Builder Mode</h2>Unleash your creativity and design your very own levels. Dive into a world of endless challenges and share your creations with fellow players, putting your platforming skills to the ultimate test.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/c601f4f003beac4ce261412ac87adb42.poster.avif?t=1730396331\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/c601f4f003beac4ce261412ac87adb42.webm?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024720/extras/c601f4f003beac4ce261412ac87adb42.mp4?t=1730396331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟  Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 74 single-player levels (including 7 bosses)<br></li><li> Innovative locomotion system<br></li><li> Online multiplayer championship<br></li><li> Customize your hero (colors, shapes, and faces)<br></li><li> Compete for the title of the fastest climber on the leaderboards for each level<br></li><li> Level Editor available in Mixed Reality</li></ul>",
